node.text: We put so much emphasis on our performance, it’s the performance of Jesus that paid for it all. He is the only one worthy to pay the price for our sins and he did. Walk with the living god hand and hand as he shows you where to go. You are his child and he is your father. You are already loved. You are already chosen.
